I.); Greater Antilles (
<collectingCountry id="F3217642FA1DFFD0C8D7B98CFBA6FF1A" box="[1007,1102,151,176]" name="Jamaica" pageId="120" pageNumber="121">Jamaica</collectingCountry>
), Lesser Antilles (
